Kathryn Crawford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kathryn_Crawford 0 Not to be confused with Katherine Crawford, a film and TV actress of the 1960s and 70s best known for co-starring in the series Gemini Man. Kathryn Crawford Moran, also spelled Katherine, (October 5, 1908 – December 7, 1980) was an American film and theatre actress of the 1920s and 1930s. She was also known as Kitty Moran. Not to_be_confused with Katherine_Crawford , a_film_and_TV_actress of the_1960s_and_70s best_known for co-starring in the_series_Gemini_Man . Kathryn_Crawford_Moran , also spelled Katherine , ( October_5_,_1908 – December_7_,_1980_) was an_American_film_and_theatre_actress of the_1920s_and_1930s . She was_also_known as Kitty_Moran .
